\fs24 \cf0 Decay
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Controls response time of the virtual vactrol (how long the strike rings out).\

\f0\b Color
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Controls balance between amplitude change and brightness filtering.\
