\f1  VCA-like behavior\
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 high values 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  stronger brightness reduction during decay\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Retrig
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Determines whether note-on events retrigger the internal LPG strike envelope.\
